                                                                                                   but other deployments and use cases may require alternative methods to provide reliable
                                                                                                   time.

                                                                                                   Related SP 800-53 Rev. 5 Controls: AU-2, AU-8, SC-45(1)

                                                                                                   Requirements that may be necessary:

                                                                                                    1. Ability to support organizationally-defined granularity in device timing
                                                                                                       measurements.
                                                                                                    2. Ability to use synchronization with a verified time source to determine the validity of
